column2: Locomotive Men Blue Cotton Linen Slim Fit Kurta
column23:
• Product Description
  • Style Note

column24:
this kurta from Locomotive is versatile and promises a great fit and comfort. It has a vibrant colour and is a great option as an off-duty attire. We think it will look best when teamed with distressed denim jeans and sandals.

  • Product Details

  • Blue kurta with stitch detailing
column29:
short sleeves with folded cuffs and button detailing at the shoulder and has a curved and vented hem

  • Material & Care

  • Cotton and linen blend
    Machine wash

  • Size & Fit

  • Slim fit
    The model (height 6' and shoulders 18") is wearing a size M
